<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Payment Received</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #27ae60;">Payment Received</h2>
        <p>Hello {{seekerName}},</p>
        <p>Great news! You have received a payment for your completed work:</p>
        <div style="background-color: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #27ae60;">
            <p><strong>Amount:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
            <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Employer:</strong> {{providerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{transactionId}}</p>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{paymentDate}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>The payment has been added to your wallet balance. You can withdraw it anytime.</p>
        <p>Thank you for your great work!<br>WorkNow Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

